title: ICE, ATF arrest 4 Puerto Rican men for stealing firearms from PRPD (ICE - US ...
text: ( Source : ICE - US Immigration and Customs Enforcement ) SAN JUAN, Puerto Rico - Four Puerto Rican men who allegedly stole 125 firearms from the Puerto Rico Police Department 's (PRPD) shooting range were arrested Friday in San Juan . U.S.
